paragraphs.title: fleta
paragraphs.text:
%sql
select concat(hour, ':', min) as time, count(msg) from owl0210 where lower(msg) rlike ('.*fleta.*|.*레타.*|.*병선.*') group by concat(hour, ':', min) order by  concat(hour, ':', min)
